            "body": "<p>参见1950年-1980年代的中国大陆以及目前朝鲜境内的朝鲜公民。</p><p><br></p><p>在国门封闭的情况下，要不从云南坐着摩托车，花200块钱偷渡出境到缅甸的佤邦赶紧跑路，要不想方设法动用关系弄到一本大陆护照和某国签证，或者某岛国投资移民护照，赶紧跑路吧。</p><p><br></p><p><a href=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/6ce4a0946f056986e26f6a299e5d041b983aa30f.jpg\" social=\"yes\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"cursor:zoom-in\"><img alt=\"001yUN6jgy6MQ5m323670&amp;690.jpg\" src=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/6ce4a0946f056986e26f6a299e5d041b983aa30f.jpg\" title=\"1541070072864795.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:540px;border-width: 0px; border-style: none; margin: 10px 0px; border-color: white;\"></a></p><p><br></p><p>这是坠吼的绝招！</p><p><br></p><p><a href=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/9db94486f815a0ba21a62d88296dbd31feb4d4e3.jpg\" social=\"yes\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"cursor:zoom-in\"><img alt=\"下载.jpg\" src=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/9db94486f815a0ba21a62d88296dbd31feb4d4e3.jpg\" title=\"1541069666782107.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:540px;border-width: 0px; border-style: none; margin: 10px 0px; border-color: white;\"></a></p><p><br></p><p>快速移民护照：</p><p><br></p><p><a href=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/ee485a471799c8ddbb801075ea94bfaef4542c81.jpg\" social=\"yes\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"cursor:zoom-in\"><img alt=\"images (1).jpg\" src=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/ee485a471799c8ddbb801075ea94bfaef4542c81.jpg\" title=\"1541069950811575.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:540px;border-width: 0px; border-style: none; margin: 10px 0px; border-color: white;\"></a></p><p><br></p><p><a href=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/8ab6baa3987ea69961c2515eb0de505909ff742e.jpg\" social=\"yes\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"cursor:zoom-in\"><img alt=\"190px-Saint_Lucian_passport.jpg\" src=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/8ab6baa3987ea69961c2515eb0de505909ff742e.jpg\" title=\"1541069811905043.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:540px;border-width: 0px; border-style: none; margin: 10px 0px; border-color: white;\"></a></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><a href=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/5e4072c10677e9d653e27c4e07f0397c92ef29dd.jpg\" social=\"yes\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"cursor:zoom-in\"><img alt=\"下载 (2).jpg\" src=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/5e4072c10677e9d653e27c4e07f0397c92ef29dd.jpg\" title=\"1541069870644236.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:540px;border-width: 0px; border-style: none; margin: 10px 0px; border-color: white;\"></a></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>千万不要拿到如下了护照：</p><p><br></p><p><a href=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/527e31adc445153046a1b393aad5ce2504b4b19a.jpg\" social=\"yes\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"cursor:zoom-in\"><img alt=\"29407589776_e519e55871_b.jpg\" src=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/527e31adc445153046a1b393aad5ce2504b4b19a.jpg\" title=\"1541069892282111.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:540px;border-width: 0px; border-style: none; margin: 10px 0px; border-color: white;\"></a></p><p><br></p><p><a href=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/6b9cfa67e725292405e613546ba213a9bc173431.png\" social=\"yes\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"cursor:zoom-in\"><img alt=\"190px-DPRK_passport.png\" src=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/6b9cfa67e725292405e613546ba213a9bc173431.png\" title=\"1541069636889206.png\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:540px;border-width: 0px; border-style: none; margin: 10px 0px; border-color: white;\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/e96ba8425322f7e8b5cf2374fa736c1d551de6e7.jpg\" social=\"yes\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"cursor:zoom-in\"><img alt=\"passport1187-001.jpg\" src=\"https://archive.is/IoZwH/e96ba8425322f7e8b5cf2374fa736c1d551de6e7.jpg\" title=\"1541069410543519.jpg\" style=\"vertical-align:middle;max-width:540px;border-width: 0px; border-style: none; margin: 10px 0px; border-color: white;\"></a></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>",
